---
title: Beef Tenderloin with Tangy Shallot Sauce plus Crispy Fingerlings & Broccoli Salad
description: Fancy pantsy, but easy peasy, this meal is dressed to impress for a weekend celebration or a weeknight treat. For your consideration: We’ve got a super tender cut of beef with a tangy-sweet shallot sauce and a side of crispy fingerling potatoes plus a roasted broccoli and mixed greens salad with a bright pickled shallot dressing. Get out the cloth napkins for a luxe experience!
